rComments: Since Justin was new, his lecture skills weren't that good. However, if you went to his office hours he was very helpful. I really enjoyed talking to him. He is the kind of dude you would want to go have a beer with. And his dreads were awesome!

Justin is a new professor...so, I'll try to cut him some slack but the truth is that this class was painfully disorganized and frustrating. Cummings knows a lot about plants but really is not a clear teacher, says wrong information, and doesn't answer questions very well. Hopefully by the time he teaches again he'll have improved!
